data.description: Welcome to the beautiful Longleaf community which is full of amenities for you and your family to enjoy. It is close to tons of great restaurants and shopping so you aren't far from any necessities. This home is packed with upgrades and is move in ready. It is on a large corner lot with a great fenced in yard for your family and pets to enjoy. Plenty of space for a pool to be added in the backyard. A metal, 50 year roof was added in 2022. Impact  PGT windows were installed in 2021. Both AC units were replaced in 2020. Gas powered water heater installed in 2020. Luxury vinyl flooring installed throughout in 2022. Upstairs bathroom fully renovated in 2023. The kitchen has newer stainless steel appliances with a 5 burner gas range and double oven.  A surge protector has added to the circuit breaker box. Wi-fi controlled irrigation system was recently installed. Ring cameras and lighting will stay in place. This property has the only fully enclosed side porch/breezeway in the neighborhood. Both the front porch and side porch have upgraded paver flooring. Custom metal railing installed on front porch in 2022. This home has 9ft ceilings throughout and feels super spacious. Recessed lighting and windows allow tons of light to enter the house. Ceiling fans have been installed in every bedroom. There is ample space for storage in this home including under stair space that was added by the current owners. The master bedroom and bathroom are located on the first floor and comes equipped with his and hers walk in closets. There is also a half bath located on the first floor for your guests. The remaining 4 bedrooms and bathroom are located upstairs to allow for privacy. There is a formal dining space located at the front of the home. The kitchen has eat in space that overlooks a large living/family room. The Longleaf community also has amazing amenities for your use, Including a pool, volleyball courts, tennis courts, basketball courts, soccer and baseball fields, multiple parks and pavilions for residents use. Make an appointment today to check out what could be YOUR NEW HOME!
